trigger.name: Memory % Committed Bytes in Use
trigger.description: This measures the ratio of Committed Bytes to the Commit Limitin other words, the amount of virtual memory in use. This indicates insufficient memory if the number is greater than 80 percent. The obvious solution for this is to add more memory.
